                <li><a href="#changelog">Changelog</a></li>
            </ul>
        </nav>
    </aside>

    <!-- MAIN CONTENT -->
    <div class="main-wrapper">
        <header>
            <h1>📦 JsonCleaner.dll</h1>
            <p>Libreria .NET per la rimozione ricorsiva di elementi JSON</p>
            <p style="font-size: 0.9em; margin-top: 10px;">Compatibile con TestStand 2019+ | <span class="highlight-new">🆕 Nuova Sintassi Semplificata!</span></p>
        </header>

        <div class="content">
            <!-- OVERVIEW -->
            <section id="overview">
                <h2>📋 Panoramica</h2>
                <p><strong>JsonCleaner</strong> è una libreria .NET che permette di rimuovere elementi da file JSON in modo ricorsivo, indipendentemente dal livello di annidamento.</p>
                
                <div class="success">
                    <strong>🎉 Novità Versione 1.1:</strong>
                    <ul style="margin-left: 20px; margin-top: 10px;">
                        <li><strong>Sintassi filtri semplificata</strong> - Zero escape, zero virgolette complicate!</li>
                        <li>Scrivi semplicemente: <code>"Occurred Equals true"</code></li>
                        <li>Niente più: <code>"[{\"Property\": \"Occurred\", ...}]"</code></li>
                    </ul>
                </div>

                <h3>Caratteristiche Principali</h3>
                <ul style="margin-left: 20px; margin-top: 10px;">
                    <li>✅ Rimozione ricorsiva di oggetti, array e proprietà</li>
                    <li>✅ <strong>Sistema di filtri condizionali con sintassi semplificata 🆕</strong></li>
                    <li>✅ Logging dettagliato opzionale</li>
                    <li>✅ Gestione memoria ottimizzata con IDisposable</li>
                    <li>✅ Protezione stack overflow (max 100 livelli)</li>
                    <li>✅ Compatibile con TestStand .NET Adapter</li>
                    <li>✅ Thread-safe e performante</li>
                </ul>

                <h3>Requisiti</h3>
                <table>
                    <tr>
                        <th>Componente</th>
                        <th>Versione Minima</th>
                    </tr>
                    <tr>
                        <td>.NET Framework / .NET</td>
                        <td>4.8 o .NET 6.0+</td>
                    </tr>
                    <tr>
                        <td>Newtonsoft.Json</td>
                        <td>13.0.3 o superiore</td>
                    </tr>
                    <tr>
                        <td>TestStand (opzionale)</td>
                        <td>2019 o superiore</td>
                    </tr>
                </table>
            </section>

            <!-- INSTALLATION -->
            <section id="installation">
                <h2>💾 Installazione</h2>
                
                <h3>File Necessari</h3>
                <div class="info">
                    <strong>📁 File da copiare sul sistema target:</strong>
                    <ul style="margin-left: 20px; margin-top: 10px;">
                        <li><code>JsonCleaner.dll</code> - Libreria principale</li>
                        <li><code>Newtonsoft.Json.dll</code> - Dipendenza JSON parser</li>
                    </ul>
                </div>

                <h3>Posizione Raccomandata</h3>
                <div class="code-block" data-lang="path">
C:\TestStand\Components\JsonCleaner\
├── JsonCleaner.dll
├── Newtonsoft.Json.dll
└── JsonCleaner_Documentation.html</div>

                <h3>Verifica Installazione</h3>
                <ol style="margin-left: 20px; margin-top: 10px;">
                    <li>Copiare i file nella cartella scelta</li>
                    <li>Aprire TestStand Sequence Editor</li>
                    <li>Creare un nuovo step con .NET Adapter</li>
                    <li>Selezionare <code>JsonCleaner.dll</code> come Assembly</li>
                    <li>Verificare che appaia la classe <code>JsonCleaner.JsonCleanerTool</code></li>
                </ol>
            </section>

            <!-- METHODS -->
            <section id="methods">
                <h2>🔧 Metodi Disponibili</h2>

                <!-- Method 1 -->
                <div class="method-card" id="method-1">
                    <h4>1. RemoveJsonElementFromString</h4>
                    <p><strong>Scopo:</strong> Rimuove elementi JSON in base al <u>contenuto/valore</u></p>
                    
                    <h4 style="margin-top: 20px;">Parametri:</h4>
                    <table>
                        <tr>
                            <th>Nome</th>
                            <th>Tipo</th>
                            <th>Direzione</th>
                            <th>Descrizione</th>
                        </tr>
                        <tr>
                            <td>inputJson</td>
                            <td>String</td>
                            <td><span class="badge badge-input">Input</span></td>
                            <td>Stringa JSON completa da processare</td>
                        </tr>
                        <tr>
                            <td>targetToRemove</td>
                            <td>String</td>
                            <td><span class="badge badge-input">Input</span></td>
                            <td>Elemento JSON da rimuovere (oggetto, array, valore)</td>
                        </tr>
                        <tr>
                            <td>outputJson</td>
                            <td>String</td>
                            <td><span class="badge badge-output">Output</span></td>
                            <td>JSON ripulito (risultato)</td>
                        </tr>
                        <tr>
                            <td>removedCount</td>
                            <td>Int32</td>
                            <td><span class="badge badge-output">Output</span></td>
                            <td>Numero di elementi rimossi</td>
                        </tr>
                        <tr>
                            <td>logOutput</td>
                            <td>String</td>
                            <td><span class="badge badge-output">Output</span></td>
                            <td>Log dettagliato operazioni</td>
                        </tr>
                        <tr>
                            <td>enableLogging</td>
                            <td>Boolean</td>
                            <td><span class="badge badge-input">Input</span> <span class="badge badge-optional">Optional</span></td>
                            <td>Abilita logging (default: false)</td>
                        </tr>
                        <tr>
                            <td>Return Value</td>
                            <td>Boolean</td>
                            <td><span class="badge badge-output">Output</span></td>
                            <td>True se operazione riuscita</td>
                        </tr>
                    </table>
                </div>

                <!-- Method 2 -->
                <div class="method-card" id="method-2">
                    <h4>2. RemovePropertyByName <span class="badge badge-new">🆕 Aggiornato v1.1</span></h4>
                    <p><strong>Scopo:</strong> Rimuove proprietà JSON in base al <u>nome</u>, con supporto filtri condizionali</p>
                    
                    <h4 style="margin-top: 20px;">Parametri:</h4>
                    <table>
                        <tr>
                            <th>Nome</th>
                            <th>Tipo</th>
                            <th>Direzione</th>
                            <th>Descrizione</th>
                        </tr>
                        <tr>
                            <td>inputJson</td>
                            <td>String</td>
                            <td><span class="badge badge-input">Input</span></td>
                            <td>Stringa JSON completa</td>
                        </tr>
                        <tr>
                            <td>propertyName</td>
                            <td>String</td>
                            <td><span class="badge badge-input">Input</span></td>
                            <td>Nome della proprietà da rimuovere (es. "Error", "Common")</td>
                        </tr>
                        <tr>
                            <td>outputJson</td>
                            <td>String</td>
                            <td><span class="badge badge-output">Output</span></td>
                            <td>JSON ripulito</td>
                        </tr>
                        <tr>
                            <td>removedCount</td>
                            <td>Int32</td>
                            <td><span class="badge badge-output">Output</span></td>
                            <td>Numero di proprietà rimosse</td>
                        </tr>
                        <tr>
                            <td>skippedCount</td>
                            <td>Int32</td>
                            <td><span class="badge badge-output">Output</span></td>
                            <td>Numero di proprietà skippate (filtri)</td>
                        </tr>
                        <tr>
                            <td>logOutput</td>
                            <td>String</td>
                            <td><span class="badge badge-output">Output</span></td>
                            <td>Log dettagliato</td>
                        </tr>
                        <tr>
                            <td>filtersJson</td>
                            <td>String</td>
                            <td><span class="badge badge-input">Input</span> <span class="badge badge-optional">Optional</span></td>
                            <td>JSON array di filtri (vecchio formato)</td>
                        </tr>
                        <tr style="background: #fef3c7;">
                            <td><strong>filtersString</strong> <span class="badge badge-new">🆕 Nuovo</span></td>
                            <td>String</td>
                            <td><span class="badge badge-input">Input</span> <span class="badge badge-optional">Optional</span></td>
                            <td><strong>Filtri sintassi semplificata</strong> (es. "Occurred Equals true")</td>
                        </tr>
                        <tr>
                            <td>enableLogging</td>
                            <td>Boolean</td>
                            <td><span class="badge badge-input">Input</span> <span class="badge badge-optional">Optional</span></td>
                            <td>Abilita logging</td>
                        </tr>
                        <tr>
                            <td>Return Value</td>
                            <td>Boolean</td>
                            <td><span class="badge badge-output">Output</span></td>
                            <td>True se successo</td>
                        </tr>
                    </table>
                </div>

                <!-- Method 3 -->
                <div class="method-card" id="method-3">
                    <h4>3. RemoveJsonElement</h4>
                    <p><strong>Scopo:</strong> Come RemoveJsonElementFromString ma opera su file fisici</p>
                    <p style="margin-top: 10px; color: #666;">Parametri identici al metodo 1, ma usa <code>inputFilePath</code> e <code>outputFilePath</code> invece di stringhe JSON.</p>
                </div>

                <!-- Method 4 -->
                <div class="method-card" id="method-4">
                    <h4>4. IsValidJson</h4>
                    <p><strong>Scopo:</strong> Verifica la validità di una stringa JSON</p>
                    
                    <table style="margin-top: 15px;">
                        <tr>
                            <th>Nome</th>
                            <th>Tipo</th>
                            <th>Direzione</th>
                        </tr>
                        <tr>
                            <td>json</td>
                            <td>String</td>
                            <td><span class="badge badge-input">Input</span></td>
                        </tr>
                        <tr>
                            <td>errorMessage</td>
                            <td>String</td>
                            <td><span class="badge badge-output">Output</span></td>
                        </tr>
                        <tr>
                            <td>Return Value</td>
                            <td>Boolean</td>
                            <td><span class="badge badge-output">Output</span></td>
                        </tr>
                    </table>
                </div>

                <h3 id="filter-system">Sistema di Filtri</h3>
                
                <div class="success">
                    <strong>🎉 NUOVO: Sintassi Semplificata v1.1!</strong>
                    <p style="margin-top: 10px;">Ora puoi usare una sintassi super semplice senza escape di virgolette!</p>
                </div>

                <h4>Formato Semplificato (RACCOMANDATO) ✅ <span class="badge badge-new">🆕 Nuovo</span></h4>
                <p>Usa il parametro <code>filtersString</code> con questa sintassi:</p>

                <div class="code-block" data-lang="syntax">
<span class="key">PropertyName Operator Value</span>

<span class="key">// Filtro singolo</span>
"Occurred Equals true"

<span class="key">// Filtri multipli (separati da punto e virgola)</span>
"Occurred Equals true; Code GreaterThan 0"

<span class="key">// Con stringhe (usa apici se contiene spazi)</span>
"Msg NotEquals ''"
"Status Contains 'Error'"
"Name StartsWith Test"</div>

                <h4>Valori Supportati</h4>
                <table>
                    <tr>
                        <th>Tipo</th>
                        <th>Esempi</th>
                        <th>Note</th>
                    </tr>
                    <tr>
                        <td>Boolean</td>
                        <td><code>true</code>, <code>false</code></td>
                        <td>Case insensitive</td>
                    </tr>
                    <tr>
                        <td>Numeri</td>
                        <td><code>0</code>, <code>10</code>, <code>3.14</code>, <code>-5</code></td>
                        <td>Int o double</td>
                    </tr>
                    <tr>
                        <td>Stringhe</td>
                        <td><code>Test</code>, <code>'Hello World'</code>, <code>"Error"</code></td>
                        <td>Apici opzionali (necessari se contiene spazi)</td>
                    </tr>
                    <tr>
                        <td>Null</td>
                        <td><code>null</code></td>
                        <td>Case insensitive</td>
                    </tr>
                </table>

                <h4 id="operators">Operatori Disponibili</h4>
                <table>
                    <tr>
                        <th>Operatore</th>
                        <th>Tipo Dati</th>
                        <th>Descrizione</th>
                        <th>Esempio</th>
                    </tr>
                    <tr>
                        <td><code>Equals</code></td>
                        <td>Tutti</td>
